request.description: Gets info of API Dummy

Gets data of single valid employee

Given 
	valid employee id
When 
	GET"http://dummy.restapiexample.com/api/v1/employee/{id}"
	and no body info
then 
	response is error "Integrity constraint violation: 1048 Column 'employee_name' cannot be null"

Gets data of single not valid employee

Given 
	valid employee id
When 
	GET"http://dummy.restapiexample.com/api/v1/employee/2"
	and no body info
then 
	response is error "Integrity constraint violation: 1048 Column 'employee_name' cannot be null"

Gets all employees



Given 

When 
	GET"http://dummy.restapiexample.com/api/v1/employees"
	and no body info
then 
	All the employees info

	POST"http://dummy.restapiexample.com/api/v1/create"

	POST"http://dummy.restapiexample.com/api/v1/create"

then 
	{"id":"74826","employee_name":"potatoe","employee_salary":"69420","employee_age":"32","profile_image":""}

Duplicate names not acceptable
